{"shardId":"UNI-FR-08","source":"E-runtime-crawl","side":"uniapp","route":"/#/pages/staking/how-it-works","url":"http://localhost:5173/#/pages/staking/how-it-works","sampledRoute":"/#/pages/staking/how-it-works","startedAt":"2026-06-13T03:42:04.354Z","status":"captured","evidence":{"snapshot":"docs/audit/shards/uni-fr-08-hash-pages-staking-how-it-works-snapshot.txt","screenshot":"docs/audit/screenshots/uni-fr-08-hash-pages-staking-how-it-works.png","snapshotInteractiveCount":0,"snapshotInteractive":[],"runtime":{"title":"","url":"http://localhost:5173/#/pages/staking/how-it-works","bodyTextLength":3374,"bodyPreview":"STAKING VAULT\nLock USDT, earn interest. Like a fixed-term deposit, but on-chain.\nChoose a lock period. Your money stays locked for that duration and earns a fixed annual rate. Unlock at maturity and claim principal + interest.\nWhat is staking?\nStaking means you agree to lock a chunk of your USDT for a set period (30, 90, 180, or 365 days). In exchange, the platform pays you a higher annual interest rate than free balance.\nThe longer you lock, the higher the rate. Once locked, your funds sit in a vault and accumulate interest day by day. At the end of the term, your principal + earned interest both come back to your wallet.\n4 plans · pick your term\nEach plan trades off lock duration for annual yield. Example: staking $100.\nTerm\nAPY\nInterest earned\n30d\n12%\n$9.86\n90d\n35%\n$86.30\n180d\n80%\n$394.","controls":[{"index":2,"tag":"uni-view","role":"","text":"What is staking?","aria":"","href":"","type":"","placeholder":"","disabled":false},{"index":4,"tag":"uni-view","role":"","text":"4 plans · pick your term","aria":"","href":"","type":"","placeholder":"","disabled":false},{"index":6,"tag":"uni-text","role":"","text":"30d","aria":"","href":"","type":"","placeholder":"","disabled":false},{"index":7,"tag":"uni-text","role":"","text":"12%","aria":"","href":"","type":"","placeholder":"","disabled":false},{"index":8,"tag":"uni-text","role":"","text"